{"type":"message","id":"11624e77","parentId":"473e372e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:39:43.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哦，我理解错了！`doubao-seed-1-8-251228` 这个模型本身不是生成视频的，它只是个大语言模型，会帮你写脚本。要生成视频需要用 `doubao-seedance-1.5` 模型，接口是 `/video/generations` 端点。\n\n让我检查一下你的模型配置，然后用正确的模型端点生成视频：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ufac7bvngwcx4oypkrwyevsz","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-gen-new && export VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY=\"cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400\" && python3 scripts/generate_video.py \"山东日照莒县浮来山风景区，清晨薄雾缭绕，千年古银杏树冠如华盖，黄叶在秋风中缓缓飘落。镜头从空中缓缓推近，穿过晨雾展现定林寺飞檐斗拱，千年古寺香烟袅袅。镜头缓缓移动，展现三大主峰鼎足而立的秀美景色，山间步道蜿蜒，秋色层林尽染，最后航拍全景展现翡翠般的浮来山镶嵌在鲁东南大地上。画面优美，镜头运动舒缓自然，秋色浓厚，禅意静谧。\" --model \"doubao-seedance-1.5\" --mode text_to_video --output 浮来山风景区.mp4 --duration 5","timeout":180}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":2890,"output":350,"cacheRead":27960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31200,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774103979382}}
