{"type":"message","id":"fb419ff8","parentId":"b41a0e4c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:40:04.470Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_z0vkfnl4jya2o5q836mn5hha","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  --first-frame \"https://example.com/image.jpg\" \\\n  --output person_smile.mp4\n```\n\n### 图生视频（Base64）\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/generate_video.py \"让图片动起来\" \\\n  --mode image_to_video_base64 \\\n  --first-frame ./input_image.png \\\n  --output animated.mp4\n```\n\n### 有声视频（首帧）\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/generate_video.py \"人物开口说话，声音洪亮\" \\\n  --mode audio_video_first_frame \\\n  --first-frame ./portrait.jpg \\\n  --audio \\\n  --output talking.mp4\n```\n\n### 有声视频（首尾帧）\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/generate_video.py \"人物从左转头到右\" \\\n  --mode audio_video_first_last_frame \\\n  --first-frame ./left.jpg \\\n  --last-frame ./right.jpg \\\n  --audio \\\n  --output turn_head.mp4\n```\n\n### Seedance-Lite 参考图\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/generate_video.py \"参考图片风格生成视频\" \\\n  --mode seedance_lite_reference \\\n  --reference-image ./style_ref.jpg \\\n  --output styled_video.mp4\n```\n\n## 工作流程\n\n1. **理解需求**：分析用户的视频需求，确定生成模式\n2. **选择模式**：文生视频、图生视频、有声视频等\n3. **优化提示词**：将用户描述扩展为详细的视频描述\n4. **执行脚本**：调用 `scripts/generate_video.py` 生成视频\n5. **等待完成**：视频生成通常需要几分钟\n6. **上传视频**：上传到飞书获取 file_key\n7. **发送视频**：使用 `message` 工具发送视频\n\n## 飞书视频上传\n\n```python\nimport requests\n\n# 获取 token（使用飞书 app_id 和 app_secret）\nresp = requests.post(\n    \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal\",\n    json={\"app_id\": \"YOUR_APP_ID\", \"app_secret\": \"YOUR_APP_SECRET\"}\n)\ntoken = resp.json()[\"tenant_access_token\"]\n\n# 上传视频\nwith open(\"video.mp4\", \"rb\") as f:\n    resp = requests.post(\n        \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/im/v1/files\",\n        headers={\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {token}\"},\n        files={\"file\": (\"video.mp4\", f, \"video/mp4\")},\n        data={\"file_type\": \"mp4\"}\n    )\nfile_key = resp.json()[\"data\"][\"file_key\"]\n\n# 发送视频\n# 使用 message 工具: {\"file_key\": \"<file_key>\"}\n```\n\n## 提示词技巧\n\n[19 more lines in file. Use offset=130 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774104004468}}
{"type":"message","id":"df8bee5c","parentId":"fb419ff8","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:40:08.123Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_hqpuqy0o8d68oyk3gdv1jhj8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-gen-new/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":32063,"output":79,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32142,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774104004472}}
{"type":"message","id":"03c5a9d0","parentId":"df8bee5c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:40:08.132Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_hqpuqy0o8d68oyk3gdv1jhj8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: video-gen\ndescription: AI视频生成与编辑，使用火山引擎 Doubao Seedance 模型。支持文生视频、图生视频、有声视频。当用户要求生成视频、制作视频、文生视频、图生视频时使用此 skill。\n---\n\n# AI 视频生成\n\n通过火山引擎 Doubao Seedance API 生成视频。\n\n## 环境变量\n\n脚本通过以下环境变量获取 API 配置：\n\n- `VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY` — 火山引擎 API Key\n- `VIDEO_GEN_BASE_URL` — API 基础地址（默认：https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3）\n\n## 支持的生成模式\n\n| 模式 | 说明 | 参数 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `text_to_video` | 文生视频 | prompt |\n| `image_to_video` | 图+文生视频（URL）| prompt + --first-frame URL |\n| `image_to_video_base64` | 图生视频（Base64）| prompt + --first-frame 路径/base64 |\n| `audio_video_first_frame` | 有声视频-首帧 | prompt + --first-frame + --audio |\n| `audio_video_first_last_frame` | 有声视频-首尾帧 | prompt + --first-frame + --last-frame + --audio |\n| `seedance_lite_reference` | Seedance-Lite 参考图 | prompt + --reference-image |\n\n## 可用模型\n\n- `doubao-seedance-1.5` — 完整版（默认）\n- `seedance-lite` — 轻量版\n\n## 使用方法\n\n### 文生视频\n\n```bash\nexport VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY=\"your-api-key\"\n\npython3 scripts/generate_video.py \"一只可爱的小猫在草地上奔跑，阳光明媚，慢动作\" \\\n  --mode text_to_video \\\n  --output cat_running.mp4\n```\n\n### 图生视频\n\n```bash\npython3 scripts/generate_video.py \"让图片中的人物转头微笑\" \\\n  --mode image_to_video \\\n  --first-frame \"https://example.com/image.jpg\" \\\n\n[98 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774104008129}}
{"type":"message","id":"42def7c2","parentId":"03c5a9d0","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:40:12.572Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根据文档，你用的API是ARK入口，模型部署在ARK平台上。那正确的方式应该是通过 `/v3/responses` 端点调用，prompt应该提示模型生成视频。让我看一下官方示例，然后调整：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_29s26oryx7jlnibm5gfvdq8r","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/fulai_request.json","content":{"model":"doubao-seed-1-8-251228","input":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"input_text","text":"生成一段展示山东日照莒县浮来山风景区的短视频：清晨薄雾缭绕，千年古银杏树冠如华盖，黄叶在秋风中缓缓飘落。镜头从空中缓缓推近，穿过晨雾展现定林寺飞檐斗拱，千年古寺香烟袅袅。镜头缓缓移动，展现三大主峰鼎足而立的秀美景色，山间步道蜿蜒，秋色层林尽染，最后航拍全景展现翡翠般的浮来山镶嵌在鲁东南大地上。画面优美，镜头运动舒缓自然，秋色浓厚，禅意静谧。"}]}]}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":3540,"output":262,"cacheRead":28984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32786,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774104008135}}
