{"type":"message","id":"6b82a8d0","parentId":"004de5fe","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:42:22.902Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"域名解析失败，那说明你所有的模型都是部署在ARK平台上，入口应该都是 `ark.cn-beijing.volces.com`。让我用正确的ARK端点格式调用视频生成：\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_875pivi2t05c7u8m2s9ud3in","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl \"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/video/generations\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"model\": \"doubao-seedance-1.5\",\n    \"prompt\": \"山东日照莒县浮来山风景区，清晨薄雾缭绕，千年古银杏树冠如华盖，黄叶在秋风中缓缓飘落。镜头从空中缓缓推近，穿过晨雾展现定林寺飞檐斗拱，千年古寺香烟袅袅。镜头缓缓移动，展现三大主峰鼎足而立的秀美景色，山间步道蜿蜒，秋色层林尽染，最后航拍全景展现翡翠般的浮来山镶嵌在鲁东南大地上。画面优美，镜头运动舒缓自然，秋色浓厚，禅意静谧。\",\n    \"aspect_ratio\": \"16:9\",\n    \"duration\": 5\n  }' | tee /tmp/ark_video_response.json","timeout":180}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1411,"output":336,"cacheRead":28984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30731,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774104137277}}
