{"type":"message","id":"3375b6d9","parentId":"30f511bb","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:42:53.628Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了！你只开通了 `doubao-seed-1-8-251228` 模型，没有 `doubao-seedance-1.5`。`doubao-seed` 本身就是文生图/文生视频模型，它通过文本输出返回视频URL，我来看看正确的提取方式。\n\n让我重新调用一次，然后完整解析JSON输出：\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3q36gmgnn5ty2vd1yn6v54v3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/responses\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400\" \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"model\": \"doubao-seed-1-8-251228\", \"input\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"input_text\", \"text\": \"生成一段展示山东日照莒县浮来山风景区的短视频：清晨薄雾缭绕，千年古银杏树冠如华盖，黄叶在秋风中缓缓飘落。镜头从空中缓缓推近，穿过晨雾展现定林寺飞檐斗拱，千年古寺香烟袅袅。镜头缓缓移动，展现三大主峰鼎足而立的秀美景色，山间步道蜿蜒，秋色层林尽染，最后航拍全景展现翡翠般的浮来山镶嵌在鲁东南大地上。画面优美，镜头运动舒缓自然，秋色浓厚，禅意静谧。\"}]}]}' > /tmp/result_full.json && python3 -c \"\nimport json\nimport re\ndata = json.load(open('/tmp/result_full.json'))\n\n# 从 choices 中提取文本\ncontent = data['choices'][0]['message']['content']\nprint('Content:', content)\n\n# 查找 JSON 中的 video_url\nimport re\nmatch = re.search(r'\\\"video_url\\\"\\\\s*:\\\\s*\\\"([^\\\"]+)\\\"', content)\nif match:\n    video_url = match.group(1)\n    print('\\\\nFound video_url:', video_url)\n    with open('/tmp/video_url.txt', 'w') as f:\n        f.write(video_url)\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":2976,"output":514,"cacheRead":30008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33498,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774104168238}}
